edu.uidaho.junicon.support.transforms

Interface IThreadResolver

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IInterpreter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractShell, CommandShell, JuniconInterpreter, TransformInterpreter, TransformSupport

    public interface IThreadResolver
    Resolver for finding the current threads unique resource instance. This can be used to have a per-thread transform cut-through, but let the interpreter handle its allocation. The default, if no resolver, is to use an inheritable thread local to hold the unique transform cut-through for each thread.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      IThreadResource getThreadResource()
      Get a unique resource instance for each thread, e.g. transform cut-through.

    • Method Detail

      • getThreadResource
